{"openapi":"3.1.0","info":{"title":"Qwen3.5-Plus OpenAI SDK Referencia Completa","description":"Referencia completa de parámetros de la API Chat Completions de Qwen3.5-Plus","license":{"name":"MIT"},"version":"1.0.0"},"servers":[{"url":"https://api.evolink.ai","description":"Producción"}],"security":[{"bearerAuth":[]}],"paths":{"/v1/chat/completions":{"post":{"summary":"Completación de Chat Qwen3.5-Plus","description":"- API Chat Completions compatible con OpenAI SDK\n- Soporta salida síncrona y streaming\n- Soporta entrada multimodal (texto, imagen, video)\n- Soporta modo de razonamiento (Chain-of-Thought)\n- Soporta búsqueda web, intérprete de código\n- Modelos compatibles: `qwen3.5-plus`, `qwen3.5-plus-2026-02-15`","operationId":"createChatCompletionQwen35PlusEsOpenAI","tags":["Generación de Chat"],"requestBody":{"required":true,"content":{"application/json":{"schema":{"$ref":"#/components/schemas/ChatCompletionRequest"},"examples":{"simple_text":{"summary":"Chat de texto simple","value":{"model":"qwen3.5-plus","messages":[{"role":"user","content":"Hola, por favor preséntate"}]}},"multi_turn":{"summary":"Conversación de múltiples turnos","value":{"model":"qwen3.5-plus","messages":[{"role":"user","content":"¿Qué es Python?"},{"role":"assistant","content":"Python es un lenguaje de programación de alto nivel..."},{"role":"user","content":"¿Cuáles son sus características principales?"}],"temperature":0.7,"max_tokens":1024}},"system_prompt":{"summary":"Prompt de sistema","value":{"model":"qwen3.5-plus","messages":[{"role":"system","content":"Eres un revisor de código profesional. Señala problemas y sugiere mejoras."},{"role":"user","content":"Por favor revisa este código: def add(a,b): return a+b"}]}},"vision":{"summary":"Comprensión de imágenes","value":{"model":"qwen3.5-plus","messages":[{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Por favor describe esta imagen"},{"type":"image_url","image_url":{"url":"https://example.com/image.jpg"}}]}]}},"thinking_mode":{"sum